The purpose of this purchase was to offer its customers more services and value, with the possibility of access to a huge international market.
This assessment and purchase service is aimed exclusively at industry professionals, such as insurance companies, appraisers, car rental companies, workshops, junkyards and car dealers, who must register before their activities.
Founded in Germany in 1996, this platform manages more than 650,000 operations across Europe, 500,000 of which in Germany alone.
Its main markets are Spain, Greece, Poland and Turkey.
